- rule_id: spans-passthrough-candidates/sent_0001-691446c7
  source:
    doc: spans_passthrough_candidates
    citation: index/accountability-goals
    span_id: Microsoft/index/accountability-goals/goal-a1-impact-assessment/sent_0001
  scope:
    actor:
    - developer
    data_domain: []
    context:
    - dev
  hazard: harm to people, organizations, or society
  conditions:
  - early in the system's development
  - when defining the product vision and requirements
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - developer shall assess the impact of the system on people, organizations, and
    society by completing an Impact Assessment.
  evidence:
  - impact assessment
  severity: high
  is_testable: true
  testability:
    reason: Requires completing an Impact Assessment — an observable artifact (document)
      that can be checked in the codebase/repo.
    evidence_signals:
    - repo_check
- rule_id: spans-passthrough-candidates/sent_0001-d74bfa6b
  source:
    doc: spans_passthrough_candidates
    citation: index/accountability-goals
    span_id: Microsoft/index/accountability-goals/goal-a1-impact-assessment/sent_0001
  scope:
    actor:
    - developer
    data_domain: []
    context:
    - dev
  hazard: harm to people, organizations, or society
  conditions:
  - early in the system's development
  - when defining the product vision and requirements
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - developer shall document the Impact Assessment using the Impact Assessment template
    provided by the Office of Responsible AI.
  evidence:
  - impact assessment template
  severity: high
  is_testable: true
  testability:
    reason: Presence of a completed Impact Assessment template file by the developer
      can be verified in the repository.
    evidence_signals:
    - repo_check
- rule_id: spans-passthrough-candidates/sent_0002-44edf2b4
  source:
    doc: spans_passthrough_candidates
    citation: index/accountability-goals
    span_id: Microsoft/index/accountability-goals/goal-a1-impact-assessment/sent_0002
  scope:
    actor:
    - org
    data_domain: []
    context:
    - dev
  hazard: development without approved impact assessment
  conditions:
  - reviewers identified according to your organization's compliance process
  - before development starts
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - Org shall review the completed Impact Assessment with the reviewers identified
    according to your organization's compliance process before development starts.
  evidence:
  - impact assessment
  severity: medium
  is_testable: true
  testability:
    reason: Can verify review approvals, reviewer identities, and timestamps showing
      review occurred before development start.
    evidence_signals:
    - repo_check
    - log_check
    - config_check
- rule_id: spans-passthrough-candidates/sent_0002-b912908e
  source:
    doc: spans_passthrough_candidates
    citation: index/accountability-goals
    span_id: Microsoft/index/accountability-goals/goal-a1-impact-assessment/sent_0002
  scope:
    actor:
    - org
    data_domain: []
    context:
    - dev
  hazard: development without approved impact assessment
  conditions:
  - approvals requested from those reviewers identified according to your organization's
    compliance process
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - Org shall secure all required approvals from those reviewers.
  evidence:
  - impact assessment
  severity: medium
  is_testable: false
  testability:
    reason: 'Unbounded: ''those reviewers'' and required approvals unspecified, so
      no objective pass/fail oracle.'
    evidence_signals:
    - config_check
    - log_check
- rule_id: spans-passthrough-candidates/sent_0003-cdb12948
  source:
    doc: spans_passthrough_candidates
